  a[label="User Input"]; b[label="Input Coordinator"]; c[label="Action Candidate"]; d[label="Bridge Validation"]; e[label="Domain Resolution"]; f[label="State Delta"]; g[label="State Commit"]; h[label="Event Bus"]; i[label="Context Packet"]; j[label="Fiction Output"]; k[label="Output Verifier"]; l[label="Replay Entry"];
